# Neurex Project Directory Structure

Registry-first React UI monorepo (pnpm + Turborepo). Install flow:

`packages/registry` → `packages/cli` → consumer project (user-owned code).

Do not blur package responsibilities. Public APIs live in `package.json` `exports` only; `dist/` is publish output; never deep-import `src/` or `dist/` from outside a package.

---

## Repository Root

```
neurex/
├── .agent/                 # Agent continuity/state (see AGENTS.md → CONTINUITY.md)
├── .cursor/rules/          # Cursor rules (*.mdc)
├── apps/                   # Workspace apps
├── docs/                   # Architecture and workflow documentation
├── packages/               # Publishable workspace packages
├── AGENTS.md               # Repo-specific agent contract (always applied)
├── README.md
├── package.json            # Root scripts (turbo orchestration)
├── pnpm-workspace.yaml     # apps/*, packages/*
├── turbo.json
├── tsconfig.json / tsconfig.base.json
├── eslint.config.mjs
└── prettier.config.mjs
```

**Ignore for source work:** `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `.turbo/`, `.pnpm-store/`, `.tmp/`

