## `packages/tokens`

Token dependency chain: **primitives → brand → semantics → component tokens**; **themes** override semantics per mode; **presets** are config only.

**Active semantic groups (11):** `color`, `action`, `border`, `elevation`, `radius`, `spacing`, `size`, `motion`, `typography`, `outline`, `layout`. Authoring for `color` lives under `semantics/color/` (merged into one `color` namespace). Canonical rules: `docs/TOKENS.md`.

```
packages/tokens/
├── src/
│   ├── primitives/       # Raw values only (color, spacing, radius, motion, z-index, shadow, …)
│   ├── brand/            # Brand palette (references primitives)
│   ├── semantics/        # Usage intent (references brand/primitives)
│   │   └── color/        # Optional subfolder; merges into top-level color.* paths
│   ├── components/       # Per-component tokens (references semantics; size/spacing primitive exception)
│   ├── themes/           # Mode overrides — same paths as semantics (border.*, action.*, color.*)
│   ├── presets/          # Preset config (not a token layer)
│   ├── resolver/         # Token resolution + layer-validation.ts (build-failing contracts)
│   ├── governance/       # Non-blocking reports (metadata, deprecation, semantic audit)
│   ├── generators/
│   │   ├── inputs/       # Source inputs for generation
│   │   ├── outputs/css/  # CSS generator
│   │   ├── outputs/dtcg/ # DTCG JSON generator
│   │   └── shared/       # Shared generator utilities
│   ├── types/            # Token/type definitions + authoring factories
│   ├── scripts/          # clean-imports, governance-report
│   └── index.ts          # Package entry
└── test/                 # resolver, generator, layer-validation, governance, semantic-audit
```

**Exports:** `.`, `./tokens.css`, `./theme.css` (generated; do not hand-write CSS).

**Elevation chain:** primitive `z-index.*` / `shadow.*` → semantic `elevation.*` → component slot tokens → UI `z-(--nx-*)` / `shadow-(--nx-*)` in `*.variants.ts`.

