## `packages/ui`

Reference implementations. Each component is a **PascalCase folder** with:

- `ComponentName.tsx`
- `ComponentName.types.ts`
- `ComponentName.variants.ts`

```
packages/ui/
├── src/
│   ├── index.ts
│   ├── utils/            # Shared UI utilities
│   └── components/       # 31 component folders (see list below)
└── test/
    ├── public-api.test.ts
    └── components/<Name>/   # Variant tests per component
```

**Components:** Accordion, Alert, AlertDialog, Avatar, Badge, Button, Card, Checkbox, Collapsible, Dialog, Drawer, Field, Fieldset, Form, Input, Menu, Meter, NumberField, Popover, Progress, RadioGroup, Select, Separator, Slider, Switch, Tabs, Textarea, Toast, Toggle, ToggleGroup, Tooltip.

Base UI (`@base-ui/react`) is internal; preserve accessibility when editing.

---

## `packages/registry`

Source of truth for what the CLI installs. **No install logic outside registry metadata.**

```
packages/registry/
├── src/
│   ├── index.ts
│   ├── registry.types.ts
│   ├── validate-registry.ts
│   ├── validate-registry-item.ts
│   ├── items/            # One file per installable item (metadata)
│   ├── styles/           # Registry style entries (e.g. theme.ts)
│   └── utilities/        # Shared utility metadata (e.g. cn.ts)
├── templates/
│   ├── components/<Name>/   # Files copied into user projects (mirrors ui layout)
│   ├── shared/utils/          # e.g. cn.ts
│   └── styles/                # tokens.css, theme.css templates
├── scripts/
│   ├── sync-component-templates.mjs   # Sync ui → templates
│   └── registry-item-generator.mjs
└── test/
    └── validate-registry.test.ts
```

**Exports:** `.`, `./templates/*` (templates ship with the package).

Every registry item must declare: files, dependencies, utilities, styles, target paths.

---

## `packages/cli`

Metadata-driven installer; depends on `@neurex/registry`.

```
packages/cli/
├── src/
│   ├── index.ts          # CLI entry (bin: neurex)
│   ├── commands/
│   │   ├── add.ts
│   │   ├── config.ts
│   │   ├── doctor.ts
│   │   ├── help.ts
│   │   ├── init.ts
│   │   ├── list.ts
│   │   ├── registry.ts
│   │   ├── status.ts
│   │   ├── uninstall.ts
│   │   ├── update.ts
│   │   └── version.ts
│   └── core/             # Installer, config, registry resolution, Tailwind/Vite setup, …
│       ├── installer.ts
│       ├── config.ts
│       ├── registry-provider.ts
│       ├── registry-resolver.ts
│       ├── tailwind-setup.ts
│       ├── vite-scaffold.ts
│       └── …
└── test/
    ├── commands/         # add, init, install-flow, registry, update
    └── core/             # installer, package-manager, tailwind-setup
```

Rules: idempotent installs, no silent overwrites, clear conflict reporting.

