## Where to Change What

| Task | Primary location |
|------|------------------|
| Token values / layers | `packages/tokens/src/` |
| Semantic organization / audit | `packages/tokens/src/governance/`, `docs/TOKENS.md` |
| Generated CSS | Build pipeline only (`packages/tokens` build) |
| Component behavior (reference) | `packages/ui/src/components/` |
| What gets installed / paths | `packages/registry/src/items/` + `templates/` |
| Install/init/update behavior | `packages/cli/src/` |
| Visual verification | `apps/playground/` |
| Architecture contracts | `docs/` + `AGENTS.md` |

After editing `packages/ui` components, run `pnpm registry:sync` to refresh registry templates when templates should match UI.

After editing overlay `*.variants.ts` stacking/shadow classes or component elevation tokens, sync registry templates and run `pnpm tokens:check`.

---

## Component File Convention (UI + registry templates)

```
ComponentName/
├── ComponentName.tsx
├── ComponentName.types.ts
└── ComponentName.variants.ts
```

Styling: Tailwind user-facing; semantic classes use `nx-` prefix (see `docs/STYLE.md`).
